0:00:00.020,0:00:03.060
Mwari achiri kutaura chimwe chinhu.

0:00:03.060,0:00:10.920
Musi weSvondo 31 August 2014, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua akapa uporofita

0:00:10.920,0:00:15.940
pamusoro pekupindira kwechiuto munyika iri mu Southern Africa.

0:00:15.940,0:00:18.260
Ngatiteererei ku mazwi ake.

0:00:18.260,0:00:22.780
Mutungamiri achanyerutswa; Ndakazvitaura.

0:00:22.780,0:00:25.820
Ndinoreva kuti, vanhu veku Southern Africa vachayeuka,

0:00:25.820,0:00:30.120
kana vasingazoreva zvisizvo zvandakataura panguva ino.

0:00:30.120,0:00:31.900
Asi parizvino, izvo zvandiri kutaura zvino -

0:00:31.900,0:00:34.320
Taurai nemazvo zvandataura; musareva nhema.

0:00:34.320,0:00:40.640
Ndiri kuona mauto - ivo vachiri pane chirongwa ichocho

0:00:40.640,0:00:46.040
kunyerusa Mutungamiri, kana muteedzeri we Mutungamiriri we nyika iyoyo.

0:00:46.040,0:00:48.400
kana Mudzimai we Mtungamiriri wenyika iyoyo.

0:00:48.400,0:00:53.720
Vari kuronga kuita izvozvo uye ivo vachiri kudisisa kuzviita.

0:00:53.720,0:00:56.960
Urongwa huri kuitika ikozvino.

0:00:56.960,0:01:00.420
Kana munyengetero usina kupiwa zvakanaka, vachabudirira.

0:01:00.420,0:01:06.300
Kana akaramba urongwa, ivo vachamuuraya.

0:01:06.300,0:01:08.240
Ndizvo zvandiri kuona.

0:01:08.240,0:01:12.400
Vanofanira kunyengeterera Southern Africa - mutungamiri.

0:01:12.400,0:01:18.200
Mwari akandiratidza nzvimbo yacho asi ini handidi kuisa chero nyika mu mhirizhonga

0:01:18.200,0:01:22.420
Asi Southern Africa - vanofanira kuvanamatira.

0:01:22.420,0:01:25.280
Vanamatirei; Mwari anovada.

